# Test: Navigation through form fields
# Use Tab and arrow keys to move between fields

# Initial view - context field focused
run
----
-- view:
Create New Ball␤
␤
Context:␤
┃ Background context for this task                          ␤
Title: (empty)␤
␤
Acceptance Criteria: (none - consider adding criteria)␤
  + (add criterion)␤
␤
Tags: (none)␤
Session: (none)␤
Model Size: (default) small medium large␤
Depends On: (none)␤
␤
Navigation: ↑/↓ fields • Tab next • ←/→ options • Enter next/add AC • Ctrl+S save • Esc cancel␤

